dataset.title: Description of a new fossil genus of conifer sawfly (Hymenoptera: Diprionidae) revealed by UV light

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article NEL, ANDRÉ, WEI, MEI-CAI, NIU, GENG-YUN, GARROUSTE, ROMAIN, JOUAULT, CORENTIN (2023): Description of a new fossil genus of conifer sawfly (Hymenoptera: Diprionidae) revealed by UV light. Palaeoentomology 6 (3): 313-320, DOI: 10.11646/palaeoentomology.6.3.14, URL: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/palaeoentomology.6.3.14
